     <body>
     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="10"/>
   <l>THou that desir'st on earth a blessed end,</l>
   <l>And seek'st the way to th'heavens to ascend,</l>
   <l>Resort to <hi>Gerard:</hi> hee'l direct the way</l>
   <l>Whereby thou mayst ascend and live for ay.</l>
   <l>Thou needst no guide, 'tis easie to be gone,</l>
   <l>All lets removed are by <hi>Winterton.</hi>
   </l>
   <l>The way's made plain, which was before obscure,</l>
   <l>That thou thereby mayst heavenly blisse procure.</l>
   <l>Endeavour then this way to walk aright:</l>
   <l>And it will lead thee to eternall light.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>T. Gore.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
